"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"The Captain called the Sergeant in.“Sarge，I just got a telegram. Private Jones’mother died yesterday. Better go to tell him and send him in to see me.”\\n\\nSo the Sergeant calls for his morning formation and lines up all the troops.“Listen up，men，”says the Sergeant.“Johnson，report to the mess hall for KP. Smith，report to Personnel to sign some papers. The rest of you men report to the Motor Pool for maintenance. Oh，by the way，Jones，your mother died，report to the commander.”\\n\\nLater that day the Captain called the Sergeant into his office.“Hey，Sarge，that was a pretty cold way to inform Jones his mother died. Couldn’t you be a bit more tactful，next time？”“Yes，sir，”answered the Sarge. A few months later，the Captain called the Sergeant in again with，“Sarge，I just got a telegram. Private McGrath’s mother died. You’d better go to tell him and send him in to see me. This time be more tactful.”So the Sergeant called for his morning formation.“Ok，men，fall in and listen up. Everybody with a mother，take two steps forward—NOT SO FAST，McGRATH！\",\"timestamp\":1641191812,\"title\":\"Be More Tactful\"},\"digest\":\"oINi-a3bA1r2kw7-xk-I89ZryMsSbAYc-yHqPUSBzyM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x104b7CCb129ffdc46e6cCd6Cd95a0FE7d40fAD72\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"X3vM0CQ5-HNETaifmbtefcb3OrGNaVQoWcnOmCpTO5M\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"1o5QCHZc6Qs1KUBQOjc0csx81FioMJfqMF0wfMwlvJ0\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"3qzLyCtf4qlFFdGUrrmBWiuhk0_QXxRK4PN3b3Whl2iWeX6KumzJGO3CfYNTCKtg1k_vwSXCaXI6V_Wpk3pNnA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x6d9bec87863cd45a0cef04af80ec4749b0b0292c146857d84b5ab526937bb5994a514c9d29a3a3a157e8bf596ad3c5f519bbb7a1daee4a644c52402b8252a7fe1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"X3vM0CQ5-HNETaif